dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. With legend of roads, railways, cable lines, waterways, department limits, neighborhood limits, limits of state forests and biological reserves, and sites of interest. Includes tourist information, rules for protecting nature. Inset to continue map : Bois de la Rochette [north extension] -- Nemours [south extension]. "Reproduction interdite."
